Sentencas: The anode materials La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-delta (LSTC, x = 0, 0.1, 0.2) with cubic structure were prepared via solid state reaction route.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs

Sentencas: The influence of Cr content on the properties of LSTC as anode and interconnect materials for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) was investigated.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs

Sentencas: The Cr-doping decreased the lattice parameter while increased the sinterability of LSTC materials.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs

Sentencas: The total electrical conductivity decreased with Cr doping level, from 230 S cm(-1) for x = 0 to 53 S cm(-1) for x = 0.2.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs

Sentencas: The total electrical conductivity exhibited good stability and recoverability in alternative atmospheres of air and 5% H-2/Ar, showing excellent redox stability.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs

Sentencas: The cell testing showed that the anode performance of LSTC was enhanced somewhat by Cr doping.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs

Sentencas: The present results indicated that the prepared La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-delta can be potential anode and interconnect materials for SOFCs.
Titulo: Electrical conductivity and cell performance of La0.3Sr0.7Ti1-xCrxO3-δ perovskite oxides used as anode and interconnect material for SOFCs
